_sText:
This is a simple Random Teleporting prefab.

Works for CS:S and HL2:DM

Once you go through the teleport trigger, there will be 3 different possible exit points, if one is blocked (by a player, npc, or prop), a red light appears above it, and will port you to another one randomly.

I added a few barrels so players can test blocking certain teleports, if they wanted to test this prefab alone.

Also very good if you have 3 players jump into a teleport at the exact same time, and don't want them all to get stuck in 1 destination.

This is an old old prefab, but i figured i might as well upload it since i havent uploaded anything in awhile.

Enjoy


EDIT*** I forgot, the screenshot posted does not show CT and T spawn points, i added them after the shot.

Plus this includes a bsp as well as vmf. so u may test for either HL2DM or CSS ;)
